       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    PSI50900.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA PSI50900.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Browse Hismensag
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE PSI50900         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE PSCDEN00 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY PSCV5090.
       COPY PSCV5091.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAL0015.
      *     OBTEM NOME DO CLIENTE NA BANKA
       COPY SXCL0380.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY PSCK0001.
       COPY PSCK0002.
      *PROCEDURE CONVERSAO DE DATAS
       COPY AQCW0005.
      *TRATAMENTO DE RETURN CODE
       COPY AQCL0001.
       COPY AQCW0009.
      *OBTEM DADOS DE UTILIZADOR
       COPY SXCL0620.
       COPY SXCL0002.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            SWITCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  SW-SWITCH.
           05 SW-CURSOR                  PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
              88 SW-CURSOR-NONE                    VALUE '0'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-1                       VALUE '1'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-2                       VALUE '2'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-3                       VALUE '3'.
              88 SW-CURSOR-4                       VALUE '3'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-PSHMENSA               PIC X(08) VALUE 'PSHMENSA'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME                PIC X(10) VALUE 'PSI50900'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *              DECLARACOES DE CURSORES DB2                     *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       01  WS-CURSOR-VARS.
           05 FILLER                     PIC X(01) VALUE SPACES.
           EXEC SQL
                DECLARE CURPST01 CURSOR FOR
                 SELECT
                       HMNCLI
                     , HMDINT
                     , HMNFIC
                     , HMTEMP
                     , HMNREG
                     , HMNALT
                     , HMOGER
                     , HMAGEN
                     , HMREF
                     , HMTREG
                     , HMTOPE
                     , HMSITC
                     , HMSITR
                     , HMCBAN
                     , HMCBAL
                     , HMCNTA
                     , HMCDIG
                     , HMMONT
                     , HMNOME
                     , HMREFTR
                     , HMDVAL
                     , HMCEST
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEEST
                 FROM PSHMENSAG
                 WHERE  HMOGER   = :PSCDEN00-HMOGER
                   AND (HMNCLI   > :PSCDEN00-HMNCLI
                    OR (HMNCLI   = :PSCDEN00-HMNCLI
                   AND  HMDINT   > :PSCDEN00-HMDINT)
                    OR (HMNCLI   = :PSCDEN00-HMNCLI
                   AND  HMDINT   = :PSCDEN00-HMDINT
                   AND  HMNFIC   > :PSCDEN00-HMNFIC)
                    OR (HMNCLI   = :PSCDEN00-HMNCLI
                   AND  HMDINT   = :PSCDEN00-HMDINT
                   AND  HMNFIC   = :PSCDEN00-HMNFIC
                   AND  HMTEMP   > :PSCDEN00-HMTEMP))
                 ORDER BY
                       HMOGER
                     , HMNCLI
                     , HMDINT
                     , HMNFIC
                     , HMTEMP
                     , HMNREG
                     , HMNALT
           END-EXEC

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE PSI50900         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '0000-MAINLINE.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO PSCV5090-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV5090-ASE               TO PSCV5091-ASE.
      *
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO PSCV5091-INDICE.
           PERFORM 1100-LIMPA-OCCURS
              THRU 1199-LIMPA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL PSCV5091-PAGINA-CHEIA.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1100-LIMPA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1100-LIMPA-OCCURS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1100-LIMPA-OCCURS.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           ADD 1                       TO PSCV5091-INDICE.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMNCLI(PSCV5091-INDICE)
           MOVE SPACES
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMNMCLI(PSCV5091-INDICE)
           MOVE SPACES
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMDINT(PSCV5091-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMNFIC(PSCV5091-INDICE)
           MOVE SPACES
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMTEMP(PSCV5091-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMNREG(PSCV5091-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMNALT(PSCV5091-INDICE)
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMDVAL(PSCV5091-INDICE)
           MOVE SPACES
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMCEST(PSCV5091-INDICE)
      *
           .
       1199-LIMPA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNCLI            TO PSCV5091-HMNCLI .
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNMCLI           TO PSCV5091-HMNMCLI.
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMDINT            TO PSCV5091-HMDINT .
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNFIC            TO PSCV5091-HMNFIC .
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMTEMP            TO PSCV5091-HMTEMP .
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNREG            TO PSCV5091-HMNREG .
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNALT            TO PSCV5091-HMNALT .
      *
           PERFORM 2010-VALIDACOES
              THRU 2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2020-OPEN
                 THRU 2029-OPEN-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2030-FETCH
                 THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT

              IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
                 IF DB2-OK
                    PERFORM 2040-CONTINUA
                       THRU 2049-CONTINUA-EXIT
                 ELSE
                    COMPUTE PSCV5091-DIMINUI-LENGTH EQUAL
                         PSCV5091-INDICE-INVERSO * PSCV5091-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE PSCV5091-LENGTH EQUAL PSCV5091-LENGTH
                         - PSCV5091-DIMINUI-LENGTH
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5091-HMNCLI-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-HMNCLI-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5091-HMNCLI-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5091-HMDINT-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-HMDINT-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5091-HMDINT-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5091-HMNFIC-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-HMNFIC-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5091-HMNFIC-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5091-HMTEMP-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-HMTEMP-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5091-HMTEMP-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5091-HMNREG-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-HMNREG-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5091-HMNREG-MSG
                    MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO PSCV5091-HMNALT-S
                    MOVE PSCK0001-HMNALT-N-EXISTS
                      TO PSCV5091-HMNALT-MSG
                 END-IF
              END-IF
              PERFORM 2070-CLOSE
                 THRU 2079-CLOSE-EXIT
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI
                 THRU 4119-OBTEM-NOME-CLI-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '4110-OBTEM-NOME-CLI'   TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS        TO SXCL0380-VERSAO
           MOVE WS-PROGNAME                TO SXCL0380-PGMC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-NOME-CLI      TO SXCL0380-TTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID          TO SXCL0380-JOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO SXCL0380-USERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ              TO SXCL0380-PGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK          TO SXCL0380-RCODE.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-NEXE         TO SXCL0380-ESTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL          TO SXCL0380-APTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-HCLI-VMSG         TO SXCL0380-HCLI.
           MOVE PSCK0002-VNCR-NVAL         TO SXCL0380-VNCR.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO SXCL0380-CLBAL.
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNCLI            TO SXCL0380-CLNCLI.

           CALL SXCL0380-ROTINA         USING SXCL0002-COMMAREA,
                                              SXCL0380-DATA.

           MOVE SXCL0380-RCODE             TO AQCW0009-RCODE.

           PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
              THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

           IF AQCL0001-COM-ERROS
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO  TO PSCV5091-HMNCLI-S
              MOVE PSCK0001-COCCLI-N-EXISTS TO PSCV5091-HMNCLI-MSG
           ELSE
              MOVE SXCL0380-DWT OF SXCL0380-WT OF SXCL0380-DATA(1)
                                           TO PSCV5091-HMNMCLI
           END-IF.
      *
       4119-OBTEM-NOME-CLI-EXIT.
           EXIT.


      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2010-VALIDACOES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2010-VALIDACOES.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2010-VALIDACOES.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           PERFORM 2100-VALIDA-GESTOR
              THRU 2199-VALIDA-GESTOR-EXIT.

       2019-VALIDACOES-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-VALIDA-GESTOR
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-VALIDA-GESTOR.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-VALIDA-GESTOR'    TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           INITIALIZE SXCL0620-DATA.
           MOVE VIAL0001-VERSAO-SYS        TO SXCL0620-VERSAO
           MOVE WS-PROGNAME                TO SXCL0620-PGMC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-TTR-VAZIO         TO SXCL0620-TTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CALLERID          TO SXCL0620-JOBNC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO SXCL0620-USERC.
           MOVE VIAL0001-MSGQ              TO SXCL0620-PGMQC.
           MOVE PSCK0002-RCODE-OK          TO SXCL0620-RCODE.
           MOVE PSCK0002-ESTR-NEXE         TO SXCL0620-ESTR.
           MOVE PSCK0002-APTR-APL          TO SXCL0620-APTR.
           MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN       TO SXCL0620-USER.

           PERFORM CALL-SXRM0620
              THRU CALL-SXRM0620-EXIT.

           MOVE SXCL0620-RCODE             TO AQCW0009-RCODE.

           PERFORM AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE
              THRU AQCP0009-TRATA-RCODE-EXIT.

           IF AQCL0001-SEM-ERROS
              IF SXCL0620-GRPR EQUAL PSCK0002-GRP-OG
                 MOVE VIAL0001-CUSER-EXTRN TO PSCV5090-HMOGER
                                              PSCV5091-HMOGER
              ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE PSCK0001-UTIL-N-GESTOR
                                           TO PSCV5091-HMOGER-MSG
                 MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO PSCV5091-HMOGER-S
              END-IF
           ELSE
              MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
              MOVE PSCK0001-ERR-AGEN-UTIL  TO PSCV5091-HMOGER-MSG
              MOVE PSCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO  TO PSCV5091-HMOGER-S
           END-IF.

       2199-VALIDA-GESTOR-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2020-OPEN
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2020-OPEN.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2020-OPEN.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNCLI            TO PSCDEN00-HMNCLI.
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMDINT            TO AQCW0005-DTX10.

           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT10INDT8-EXIT.

           MOVE AQCW0005-DT98              TO PSCDEN00-HMDINT.
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNFIC            TO PSCDEN00-HMNFIC.
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMTEMP            TO PSCDEN00-HMTEMP.
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNREG            TO PSCDEN00-HMNREG.
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMNALT            TO PSCDEN00-HMNALT.
           MOVE PSCV5090-HMOGER            TO PSCDEN00-HMOGER.

           SET SW-CURSOR-NONE              TO TRUE.

           IF SW-CURSOR-NONE
              SET SW-CURSOR-1 TO TRUE
           END-IF

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN SW-CURSOR-1
                    EXEC SQL
                        OPEN CURPST01
                    END-EXEC
           END-EVALUATE.

           MOVE CON-PSHMENSA               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2029-OPEN-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2030-FETCH
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2030-FETCH.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2030-FETCH.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN SW-CURSOR-1
                    EXEC SQL
                       FETCH CURPST01
                       INTO
                           :PSCDEN00-HMNCLI
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMDINT
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMNFIC
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMTEMP
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMNREG
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMNALT
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMOGER
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMAGEN
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMREF
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMTREG
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMTOPE
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMSITC
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMSITR
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMCBAN
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMCBAL
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMCNTA
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMCDIG
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMMONT
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMNOME
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMREFTR
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMDVAL
                         , :PSCDEN00-HMCEST
                         , :PSCDEN00-CUSERID
                         , :PSCDEN00-HTIMEEST
                    END-EXEC


           END-EVALUATE.

           MOVE CON-PSHMENSA               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

       2039-FETCH-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                       2040-CONTINUA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2040-CONTINUA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2040-CONTINUA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE ZEROES                     TO PSCV5091-INDICE.
           PERFORM 2050-TRATA-OCCURS
              THRU 2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT
             UNTIL DB2-NOTFND
                OR PSCV5091-PAGINA-CHEIA
                OR NOT VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF NOT PSCV5091-PAGINA-CHEIA
                    COMPUTE PSCV5091-INDICE-INVERSO EQUAL
                         PSCV5091-INDICE-INVERSO - PSCV5091-INDICE
                    COMPUTE PSCV5091-DIMINUI-LENGTH EQUAL
                         PSCV5091-INDICE-INVERSO * PSCV5091-LENGTH-OCCUR
                    COMPUTE PSCV5091-LENGTH EQUAL PSCV5091-LENGTH -
                         PSCV5091-DIMINUI-LENGTH
                    SET  VIAL0002-FIM-CONSULTA TO TRUE
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2049-CONTINUA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2050-TRATA-OCCURS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2050-TRATA-OCCURS.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2050-TRATA-OCCURS.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           ADD 1                       TO PSCV5091-INDICE.
           MOVE PSCDEN00-HMNCLI
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMNCLI(PSCV5091-INDICE).
           MOVE PSCDEN00-HMDINT            TO AQCW0005-DT98.

           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10-EXIT.

           MOVE AQCW0005-DTX10
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMDINT(PSCV5091-INDICE).
           MOVE PSCDEN00-HMNFIC
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMNFIC(PSCV5091-INDICE).
           MOVE PSCDEN00-HMTEMP
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMTEMP(PSCV5091-INDICE).
           MOVE PSCDEN00-HMNREG
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMNREG(PSCV5091-INDICE).
           MOVE PSCDEN00-HMNALT
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMNALT(PSCV5091-INDICE).
           MOVE PSCDEN00-HMDVAL            TO AQCW0005-DT98.

           PERFORM AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10
              THRU AQCP0005-CONV-DT8INDT10-EXIT.

           MOVE AQCW0005-DTX10
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMDVAL(PSCV5091-INDICE).
           MOVE PSCDEN00-HMCEST
             TO PSCV5091-D-HMCEST(PSCV5091-INDICE).
      *
           PERFORM 2030-FETCH
              THRU 2039-FETCH-EXIT.
      *
       2059-TRATA-OCCURS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                     2070-CLOSE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2070-CLOSE.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2070-CLOSE.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           EVALUATE TRUE
               WHEN SW-CURSOR-1
                    EXEC SQL
                        CLOSE CURPST01
                    END-EXEC
           END-EVALUATE.

       2079-CLOSE-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE PSCV5091-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE PSCV5091-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE PSCV5091-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE PSCV5091-INDICE            TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
      *PROCEDURE CONVERSAO DE DATAS
           COPY AQCP0005.
      *PROCEDURE TRATAMENTO DE DEBUG
       COPY VIAP0016.
      *OBTEM DADOS DE UTILIZADOR
       COPY SXCR0620.
      *TRATAMENTO DE RETURN CODE
       COPY AQCP0009.
